{subhead}Be Afraid{def}
{left}
{pp}
 This may not affect the Amiga Community yet, but  the  implications  of
 what's contained within this article are scary enough even now. One of
 the worlds largest free ISPs now makes it a condition of service  that
 they  be  allowed access to your machine in order for them to make use
 of it for their own use.
{pp}
 Unbelievable? Well it's happening now!
